text: Stammheim is a new municipality in Andelfingen in the canton of Zurich in Switzerland. On 1 January 2019 the municipalities Oberstammheim, Unterstammheim and Waltalingen joined together to become new municipality Stammheim. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Andelfingen Category:2010s establishments in Switzerland Category:2019 establishments in Europe
